@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000

### Health

GET {{baseUrl}}/health


### Entities

# Criar entidade
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/entities
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Millennium Falcon"
}

###

# Criar entidade — validação: nome vazio (espera 400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/entities
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": ""
}

###

# Listar entidades (padrão: page=1, limit=20)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/entities

###

# Listar entidades — com paginação
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/entities?page=1&limit=5

###

# Listar entidades — filtrar por status
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/entities?status=active

###

# Listar entidades — filtrar por status suspenso
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/entities?status=suspended

###

# Listar entidades — busca por nome
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/entities?search=falcon

###

# Listar entidades — combinar filtros
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/entities?page=1&limit=10&status=active&search=falcon

###

# Ranking de criticidade (top 10)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/entities/ranking


### Events

# Registrar evento — severity info
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/events
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "entity_id": 1,
  "external_id": "evt-001",
  "severity": "info",
  "payload": { "message": "Sistema iniciado" }
}

###

# Registrar evento — severity warning
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/events
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "entity_id": 1,
  "external_id": "evt-002",
  "severity": "warning",
  "payload": { "cpu": 87, "threshold": 80 }
}

###

# Registrar evento — severity critical
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/events
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "entity_id": 1,
  "external_id": "evt-003",
  "severity": "critical",
  "payload": { "reason": "Falha no hiperdrive" }
}

###

# Registrar evento — idempotência (mesmo external_id, espera 200 + idempotent: true)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/events
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "entity_id": 1,
  "external_id": "evt-001",
  "severity": "info",
  "payload": {}
}

###

# Registrar evento — validação: severity inválido (espera 400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/events
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "entity_id": 1,
  "external_id": "evt-004",
  "severity": "ultra-critical",
  "payload": {}
}

###

# Registrar evento — validação: entity_id ausente (espera 400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/events
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "external_id": "evt-005",
  "severity": "info"
}

###

# Registrar evento — entity inexistente (espera 404)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/events
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "entity_id": 99999,
  "external_id": "evt-ghost",
  "severity": "info",
  "payload": {}
}


### SSE — colar no browser ou usar curl

# GET {{baseUrl}}/api/events/stream
# (REST Clients normalmente não suportam SSE — use o browser ou:)
# curl -N http://localhost:3000/api/events/stream
